{
  "stem": "353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father and my mother and my sister were-- we hide them in this building, where we live, and put them on-- in hiding, so nobody could find them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we heard, my brother and me, when we heard about there will be deportation and the ghetto will be liquidated, so we went home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As I-- my brother run home-- and I-- I approached to the house, the whole family of mine was already in-- in the room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, I said, why did you came out?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did you-- didn't stay in the-- in the place where you were hiding?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the SS people came in and throw us on the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the street were staying the big SS people, the-- the officers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I handed them the-- the bescheinigung, the SS bescheinigung, that I am a-- a auto mechanic for SS [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very, very important for German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of those officers took the-- the bescheinigung and tore it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, you're going to go together with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went on Plac Zgody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here, I was approved and nothing was helping, even the-- even the piece of paper who came with the-- with the hakenkreuz on it, with all kind of stamps from the-- from the Nazis and from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing was helping me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to clean up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They clean up even those people who they were very needed for them to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he tore up the papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put us on the Plac Zgody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, Plac Zgody, with my father, with my brother, sister, and-- and my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met, sitting on the floor, my wife's mother, with two sisters.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
